2017-07-17 11:13:05.735799 - DEBUG --> 
            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_user_id_2' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (1)
                        ) OR 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_role_administrator' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (1)
                        ) OR 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_role_bbp_keymaster' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (1)
                        )) AND (l.form_id IN (1) AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY (l.id+0) DESC
                    LIMIT 0,150
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

            ORDER BY filtered.sort

            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l

                FROM

                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id

2017-07-17 11:39:11.428915 - DEBUG --> 
            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (l.form_id=1 AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY (l.id+0) DESC
                    LIMIT 0,20
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

            ORDER BY filtered.sort

2017-07-17 12:10:08.056133 - DEBUG --> 
            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (l.form_id=1 AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY (l.id+0) DESC
                    LIMIT 0,20
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

            ORDER BY filtered.sort

2017-07-17 15:04:40.152585 - DEBUG --> 
            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_user_id_2' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (1)
                        ) OR 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_role_administrator' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (1)
                        ) OR 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_role_bbp_keymaster' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (1)
                        )) AND (l.form_id IN (1) AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY (l.id+0) DESC
                    LIMIT 0,150
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

            ORDER BY filtered.sort

2017-07-17 15:11:18.583142 - DEBUG --> GFFormsModel::trim_form_meta_values(): Starting. 
2017-07-17 15:11:18.583456 - DEBUG --> GFFormsModel::trim_conditional_logic_values(): Starting. 
2017-07-17 15:11:22.182183 - DEBUG --> 
            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value >= '2017-01-01')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value < '2017-12-31')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_step_status_1' AND meta_value = 'approved'
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND l.created_by = '2') AND (l.form_id=1 AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY (l.id+0) DESC
                    LIMIT 0,20
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

            ORDER BY filtered.sort

2017-07-17 15:12:18.321764 - DEBUG --> 
            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value >= '2017-01-01')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value < '2017-12-31')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_step_status_1' AND meta_value = 'approved'
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND l.created_by = '40') AND (l.form_id=1 AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY (l.id+0) DESC
                    LIMIT 0,20
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

            ORDER BY filtered.sort

            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_user_id_2' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (1)
                        ) OR 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_role_administrator' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (1)
                        ) OR 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_role_bbp_keymaster' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (1)
                        )) AND (l.form_id IN (1) AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY (l.id+0) DESC
                    LIMIT 0,150
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

2017-07-17 15:56:35.631458 - DEBUG --> 
            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (l.form_id=1 AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY l.id DESC
                    LIMIT 0,20
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

            ORDER BY filtered.sort

            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_user_id_2' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (2,1)
                        ) OR 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_role_administrator' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (2,1)
                        ) OR 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_role_bbp_keymaster' AND meta_value = 'pending'
                        AND form_id IN (2,1)
                        )) AND (l.form_id IN (2,1) AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY (l.id+0) DESC
                    LIMIT 0,150
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

            ORDER BY filtered.sort

2017-07-18 14:20:59.928997 - DEBUG --> 
            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value >= '2017-01-01')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value < '2017-12-31')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_step_status_1' AND meta_value = 'approved'
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND l.created_by = '115') AND (l.form_id=1 AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY (l.id+0) DESC
                    LIMIT 0,20
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

            ORDER BY filtered.sort

            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (

                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value >= '2017-01-01')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND

                        AND form_id=1

                        AND form_id=1

            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (

                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id

                        l.id IN
                        (

                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value >= '2017-01-01')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND

                        AND form_id=1

            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN

                FROM
                (

                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id

                        l.id IN
                        (

                        lead_id

            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (

                FROM
                (

                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id

                        l.id IN
                        (

                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail

                        ) AND

                        AND form_id=1

            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (

                FROM
                (

                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id

                        l.id IN
                        (

                        lead_id

            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value >= '2017-01-01')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value < '2017-12-31')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_step_status_1' AND meta_value = 'approved'
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND l.created_by = '2') AND (l.form_id=1 AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY (l.id+0) DESC
                    LIMIT 0,20
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

            SELECT filtered.sort, l.*, d.field_number, d.value
            FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value >= '2017-01-01')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value < '2017-12-31')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND 
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead_meta
                        WHERE meta_key='workflow_step_status_1' AND meta_value = 'approved'
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND l.created_by = '40') AND (l.form_id=1 AND l.status = 'active')
                    ORDER BY (l.id+0) DESC
                    LIMIT 0,20
                ) page
            ) filtered ON filtered.id = l.id

            ORDER BY filtered.sort

            INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
            INNER JOIN
            (
                SELECT @rownum:=@rownum + 1 as sort, id
                FROM
                (
                    SELECT distinct l.id
                    FROM 5gx0Q_rg_lead l
                    INNER JOIN 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail d ON d.lead_id = l.id
                    
                    WHERE (
                        l.id IN
                        (
                        SELECT
                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value >= '2017-01-01')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND 
                        l.id IN
                        (

                        lead_id
                        from 5gx0Q_rg_lead_detail
                        WHERE (field_number BETWEEN '1.9999' AND '2.9999' AND value < '2017-12-31')
                        AND form_id=1
                        ) AND

                        AND form_id=1
